title: Got a S- on a champ that is not mastery level 5 and got no token

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body: I got done playing a normal game on summoners rift with Xayah. After the game I saw I got an S- but I didn't get any token. Why is that? Please and thank you.

replies.body: I've got your account pulled up now, and it looks like your Xayah is only at mastery level 3. You won't start earning [**Mastery Tokens**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204211284) until you've leveled her up to mastery level 5.
Ohhh Ok I get it. Thank you.
You would have needed to achieve level 5 prior to receiving an S- to obtain a Mastery 6 token. You would need to achieve S or S+ to obtain a Mastery 7 token.
